headline: Keysight Introduces Optical Automotive Ethernet Transmitter Test Solution for nGBASE-AU Standard
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., October 14, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) introduced the AE6980T nGBASE-AU Optical Automotive Ethernet Transmitter Test Solution, the industry’s first platform to qualify next-generation optical automotive Ethernet PHYs in compliance with the IEEE 802.3cz standard. Keysight unveiled the solution at the 2025 IEEE SA Ethernet & IP @ Automotive Technology Day in Toulouse, France.
